-- Iran Navy Chief Says Blocking Hormuz ‘Easy,’ Press TV Reports
-- B y   R o b e r t   T u t t l e
-- 2011-12-28T12:46:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-28/iran-navy-chief-says-blocking-hormuz-easy-press-tv-reports.html
Iran  can block the Strait of Hormuz
if necessary,  Press TV said , citing Navy Commander Habibollah
Sayyari.  “Closing the Strait of Hormuz is very easy for Iranian
naval forces,” Iran’s Press TV cited Sayyari as saying. “Iran
has comprehensive control over the strategic water way.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
